The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The focus is on safe reinforcement learning, which involves constraints on the policy optimization problem, making it relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses optimal control, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY), and multi-agent reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of both machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.MA).
